Package: r2sas
Type: Package
Title: Convert R Code and Analysis to SAS Language
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-05-21
Authors@R: person("Herald", "Agent", email = "herald@optiplex-node-01", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Translates common R expressions, data manipulation idioms, and
    statistical model calls into equivalent SAS language syntax. Supports
    conversion of data.frame operations, dplyr verbs, base R statistics
    (lm, glm, t.test, chisq.test, etc.), and basic ggplot2 chart calls
    into SAS DATA steps and PROC steps. Designed as a learning aid and
    migration helper for analysts moving between R and SAS.
